{"tid":1536240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對於大學生罷課嘅小小提議","createTime":"2019-09-03T15:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T15:47:30.000Z","uid":188231,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5f44d6ecef2878a01599d7cade08e56403ab88ed","tid":1536240,"uid":188231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:10:12.000Z","msg":"其實大學罷課除咗罷課不罷學之外<br />\n仲可以做返啲針對學校內政嘅行動<br />\n大家都有講過<br />\n學校喺嗰政府體制入面 <br />\n癱瘓或者阻礙佢嘅行政運作無形間都向緊嗰政權施壓<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以我建議大家可以就住自己間學校有啲咩問題再搞返相應活動</span></span> 以達到光復校園之效<br />\n自己讀中大 就以中大為例<br />\n段崇智潛水 迫佢回應都好<br />\n中大同北京大學合辦嘅送中中文系雙學位課程<br />\n以及就住中醫學院嘅同學被迫要到中國實習嘅風險<br />\n當然仲有更多啦 大家可以就住呢個方向舉行一啲校內示威、集會等<br />\n<br />\n除咗中大之外 其他大學都有佢地自己嘅問題<br />\n例如poly 校長反對罷課 之前嘅連儂牆事件同不合理嘅處分<br />\n城大建築副教授「女生想安全別出去」嘅言論 先前校友師生集會校長唔出席<br />\n浸大以普通話試作畢業要求等 以及及後對示威同學嘅不合理處分<br />\n當然其他u都會有佢地自己問題 可以俾返校內同學自己研究 呢到舉啲例子啫<br />\n<br />\n你問針對呢啲事搞活動有乜用？<br />\n一嚟 可以令到大家嘅參與度大咗 同時都向校方行政施壓<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最緊要嘅一點係 支援俾校方打壓嘅中學生</span></span><br />\n我地要俾信心同幫佢地打支強心針 一齊對抗校方嘅打壓/不公義 同佢地同路<br />\n<br />\n以上係一啲建議 希望可以幫到大家手 <br />\n令到罷課可以做得更多野 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"3bc0a865f1c5999c190b8b40522c19916495f45a","tid":1536240,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:11:21.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f9b6908667835f4416a2959ba73bc18457b0c9b","tid":1536240,"uid":64702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:12:15.000Z","msg":"不過呢個係單一議題事件???"},{"pid":"372632c0d0eabc9ad031b8be61fe4628676b01e7","tid":1536240,"uid":188231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:12:27.000Z","msg":"同埋補充返<br />\n大家都眼見有唔少大學生都有繼續返學<br />\n建議罷咗課嘅學生其實可以做多少少文宣功夫<br />\n例如去自己上嘅course嗰班嘅門口 <br />\n喺啲上堂前或者落咗堂之後係門口派下傳單<br />\n做下校內文宣咁"},{"pid":"75a734aabafcf752fce0215a31f401b8f8040747","tid":1536240,"uid":188231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:13:36.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374dca6994d5a550d436c2b9b3ea888bbccfc79b","tid":1536240,"uid":167883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:14:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Renq43y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRenq43y.jpg&h=bb73b46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X2FTuve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2FTuve.jpg&h=3a22dffd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xbetioz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxbetioz.jpg&h=8f95a040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1513398/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1513398/page/1</a><br />\n如何不仇警？"},{"pid":"60b57734fe54fba113888832c72bded17d4fa8b4","tid":1536240,"uid":188231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f9b6908667835f4416a2959ba73bc18457b0c9b","tid":1536240,"uid":64702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:12:15.000Z","msg":"不過呢個係單一議題事件???"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:15:44.000Z","msg":"其實冇話單唔單一<br />\n之所以出現以上看似單一議題嘅事件其實都源於學校內政有問題<br />\n當然 外面嘅抗爭活動必定參加<br />\n但校內嘅運動我地可以做多啲"},{"pid":"abac7cfc56bb3a74dd142c92ab968b3af097176d","tid":1536240,"uid":188231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:16:52.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者就算大家認為我建議唔夠好的話都可以講下有啲乜可以做<br />\n我拋下磚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fb796141f489ff14275e4b7345284121094d58","tid":1536240,"uid":188231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:17:27.000Z","msg":"再自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf8106e06395600c27588efa80a64526178a16e","tid":1536240,"uid":188231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:18:51.000Z","msg":"再推下"},{"pid":"b7d32bb259c63039930f2459ee82370cf914aae0","tid":1536240,"uid":188231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:19:18.000Z","msg":"六連推"},{"pid":"7eee878e9b57328a0cb27820fb43fb5bb79155ee","tid":1536240,"uid":188231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:20:26.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"a0ff82ba9f54bff4e47d0ea6ff2cc81195cf52a7","tid":1536240,"uid":219736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:20:31.000Z","msg":"重點係就算間u有集